<p>Whether you have given thousands of talks in front of a large audience or you have moderate experience in public speaking, if you have the practical knowledge to share ‚Äî please, do it, <a href="https://europe.wordcamp.org/2022/call-for-speakers/">apply to speak</a>!</p>
<p>WordCamp Europe organizers will soon be hosting an online Q&amp;A session where you can ask questions and get guidance on how to raise the chance for your application to be selected. Keep an eye out <a href="https://europe.wordcamp.org/2022">on the WCEU website </a>to be notified of the same.</p>
